  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together minari, char-grill-yang, lamb, onion, garlic, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Form the mixture into 4-6 patties, depending on desired size.",
    "Brush the grill or grill pan with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the patties for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Let the patties rest for 2-3 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
